beer.beer_description: A mighty fine Pale Ale, oozing intense citrus and tropical fruit hop aroma, this pale ale gives your IPA a run for its money. With almost 10grams of our favourite hops per litre of beer, you know this beer is tasty. It’s brewed with very restrained malt character, resulting in a crisp and clean brew with a nice snappy bitterness to finish.
